Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.42,0:00:04.21,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,The Kamisato Clan's future, the duties of the Yashiro Commission...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.98,0:00:09.01,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,My brother should not bear these burdens alone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.71,0:00:24.02,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,This belief is what has led me to this duel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:30.13,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,"Check"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.82,0:00:35.95,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,When the Tsubaki is in season
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.54,0:00:39.54,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,I always have the same dream
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:45.34,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,My mother is with me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.51,0:00:48.16,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,And I am at peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.62,0:00:53.44,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,Maybe, somewhere deep down inside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:01:00.08,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,The carefree days of family time have not ended for me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.16,0:01:09.92,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,But just as flowers wither
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:14.30,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,I too must awaken from my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.72,0:01:28.45,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,The Kamisato Art of Tachi Jutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.96,0:01:33.39,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,Still like the morning dew, swift like lightning...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.30,0:01:43.95,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,Something stirs within me, perhaps the echo of a fond dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.42,0:01:48.75,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,But there it stays, day after day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.85,0:02:00.27,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,Pushing me to overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:05.86,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,And tempering my blade
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:16.59,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,That was the first time I bested Brother in a duel
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.38,0:02:27.04,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,It was also the moment that the Shirasagi Himegimi was born
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:36.35,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,It's show time, Ayaka
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:41.15,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,The fireworks have started, everyone's waiting for you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:46.59,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,It was your wish to take over this side of things, if I recall?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.82,0:02:49.39,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,Heh, sorry, Ayato
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:02:58.27,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,We pray to our god:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:02.42,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,May all our dreams endure forever
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.13,0:03:05.73,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,Narukami Island
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:09.14,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,Let the festival begin!
